```
Doing analysis at TEMP = 100.000000 and TNOM = 27.000000

Node                                   Voltage
----                                   -------
vdd                                       1.62
net1                                       1.8
vdd#branch                          4.1529e-05   <- leakage jumped from 0.32 nA to 41 µA!

